# GoPortal Frontend — Master Rule

## Monorepo layout — each folder has exactly 1 responsibility

```
frontend/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/          ENTRY POINT for browser. Only contains: main.tsx, App.tsx, vite.config.ts, index.html.
│   │                 MUST NOT contain components, hooks, or business logic.
│   └── desktop/      ENTRY POINT for Electron. Only contains: main.tsx, vite.config.ts, index.html,
│                     electron/main.ts, electron/preload.ts.
│                     MUST NOT contain components, hooks, or business logic.
│
├── packages/
│   ├── ui/           DESIGN SYSTEM. Contains Shadcn components, globals.css, cn() utility.
│   │                 MUST NOT contain business logic, API calls, or state.
│   │
│   ├── app-core/     ROUTING + LAYOUT + PROVIDERS. Contains AppShell, AuthLayout, React Router,
│   │                 QueryClient provider, ErrorBoundary.
│   │                 MUST NOT contain feature-specific UI or API calls.
│   │
│   ├── features/     EACH SUBFOLDER = 1 INDEPENDENT FEATURE.
│   │   ├── auth/         Login, Register, ForgotPassword
│   │   ├── chat/         MessageList, MessageBubble, MessageInput, EmojiPicker
│   │   ├── channels/     ChannelList, ChannelItem, CreateChannelModal
│   │   ├── server-list/  ServerRail, ServerIcon, CreateServerModal
│   │   ├── user-profile/ UserAvatar, UserPopover, UserSettingsModal
│   │   ├── voice/        VoiceChannel, VoiceControls (VOICE_ENABLED=false)
│   │   ├── notifications/ NotificationToast
│   │   ├── file-upload/  FileDropZone, UploadProgress
│   │   └── dashboard/    DashboardView (mock), mockData.ts
│   │
│   ├── store/        GLOBAL STATE (Zustand). Each file = 1 slice.
│   │                 auth.store.ts, chat.store.ts, server.store.ts, ui.store.ts, voice.store.ts
│   │                 MUST NOT contain UI components.
│   │
│   ├── services/     DATA ACCESS LAYER. Axios client, repository functions, Socket.io, TanStack Query.
│   │                 MUST NOT contain UI components or Zustand stores.
│   │
│   ├── config/       ENV VARS + CONSTANTS + FEATURE FLAGS. Only exports values, no logic.
│   │
│   └── types/        SHARED TYPESCRIPT TYPES. models.ts is source of truth for domain types.
│                     MUST NOT import from any other package in the monorepo.
│
└── tooling/          SHARED CONFIG. eslint, tailwind base, tsconfig base.
                      MUST NOT contain runtime code.
```

## Dependency graph — unidirectional, NO reverse imports

```
apps/*
  └─► app-core
        └─► features/*
              └─► store
              └─► services
              └─► ui
              └─► types
              └─► config

types      (imports nothing from monorepo)
config     (imports nothing from monorepo)
ui         (imports only types from monorepo)
services   (imports only types, config)
store      (imports only types, config, services)
```

Violating dependency graph = REJECT the task, explain why.

## When creating a new file — mandatory checklist

1. Which layer does this file belong to? (UI primitive / layout / feature / store / service / type)
2. Place it in the correct package according to the table above
3. Use import paths with `@goportal/*`, never use relative paths between packages
4. Do NOT create new folders outside the structure defined above
